    # Function to add water in pot and ensure it is on the stove
    achieve has_water(pot)
    achieve on(pot, stove)

behavior boil_vegetables(pot:item, stove:item):
    body:
        water_and_boiling_pot(pot, stove)
        achieve is_on(stove)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind pot: item where:
            is_pot(pot) and close_char(char, pot)
        
        bind stove: item where:
            is_stove(stove) and close_char(char, stove)
        
        boil_vegetables(pot, stove)

behavior find_stove_with_pot(stove:item):
    body:
        achieve inside_char(char, stove)
        achieve close_char(char, stove)
        # Approach the stove that has a pot

        # Make sure pot is on stove

        # Ensure the stove is on for boiling

        # Confirm the pot has water
        achieve has_water(pot)
